ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT T.DES_MOVIMIENTO, /*1*//*# mov_tipo */ CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 103), /*2*//*# mov_fecha_dma */ CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), FEC_AUTORIZACION, 103), /*3*//*# mov_fecha_autorizacion */ U.NOMBRE, /*4*//*# mov_usuario_nombre */ U.INICIALES, /*5*//*# mov_usuario_sigla */ U.Email, /*6*//*# mov_usuario_email */ U.Telefono, /*7*//*# mov_usuario_telefono */ DIR.DES_DIREC, /*8*//*# mov_usuario_direccion */ SUBDIR.DES_SUBDIREC, /*9*//*# mov_usuario_subdireccion */ DEP.NOMBRE, /*10*//*# mov_usuario_departamento */ OBS1, /*11*//*# mov_obs1 */ OBS2, /*12*//*# mov_obs2 */ OBS3, /*13*//*# mov_obs3 */ OBS4, /*14*//*# mov_obs4 */ OBS5, /*15*//*# mov_obs5 */ OBS_MOVIMIENTO, /*16*//*# mov_observ */ dias_cal_vencimiento, /*17*//*# mov_dias_vencimiento */ M.cod_secuencia, /*18*//*# mov_secuencia_codigo */ ser_secuencia, /*19*//*# mov_secuencia_serie */ num_secuencia /*20*//*# mov_secuencia_numero */ FROM USUARIO U LEFT OUTER JOIN SUBDIRECCION SUBDIR ON U.COD_DIREC = SUBDIR.COD_DIREC AND U.COD_SUBDIREC = SUBDIR.COD_SUBDIREC LEFT OUTER JOIN DEPARTAMENTO DEP ON U.COD_DIREC = DEP.COD_DIREC AND U.COD_SUBDIREC = DEP.COD_SUBDIREC AND U.COD_DEPTO = DEP.COD_DEPTO , MOVIMIENTO M, TIPO_MOVIMIENTO T, DIRECCION DIR WHERE M.TIP_TRAMITE = :GVstrTIP_TRAMITE AND M.NUM_TRAMITE = :GVnNUM_TRAMITE AND M.SEC_MOVIMIENTO = :GVnSEC_MOVIMIENTO AND M.TIP_MOVIMIENTO = T.TIP_MOVIMIENTO AND M.USER_ID_CAPT = U.USER_ID AND U.COD_DIREC = DIR.COD_DIREC

SELECT ser_secuencia /*1*//*# mov_ult_resol_serie */, num_secuencia /*2*//*# mov_ult_resol_numero */ FROM MOVIMIENTO M WHERE /* selecciono los movimientos del tramite que sean anteriores al parametro */ M.TIP_TRAMITE = :GVstrTIP_TRAMITE AND M.NUM_TRAMITE = :GVnNUM_TRAMITE AND M.SEC_MOVIMIENTO <= :GVnSEC_MOVIMIENTO AND /* selecciono solamente resoluciones */ M.cod_secuencia = 'RESOL' /* ordeno para obtener la ultima resolucion del tramite */ ORDER BY FEC_MOVIMIENTO DESC
select {mov_opciones_especial} /*# mov_opciones */

ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CASE WHEN {mov_fecha_dma} IS NULL THEN NULL /*ELSE CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {mov_fecha_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {mov_fecha_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(DATEPART(YYYY, CONVERT(DATETIME, {mov_fecha_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) */ ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, {mov_fecha_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, {mov_fecha_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, {mov_fecha_dma}, 103)) END /*# mov_fecha_texto */

SELECT CASE subtip_solicitud WHEN 'S2' THEN 'Artículos 28, 29, 30, 31, 42 y 58' WHEN 'S5' THEN 'Artículos 28, 29, 30, 31, 42 y 58' WHEN 'S1' THEN 'Artículos 28, 29, 30, 31, 42 y 58' WHEN 'S4' THEN 'Artículos 28, 29, 30, 31, 42 y 58' WHEN 'U1' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'U4' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'U3' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'U2' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'S3' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'S6' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'U5' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'U6' THEN 'Artículos 23, 24, 25, 26, 27 y 42' WHEN 'TR' THEN 'Artículos 6, 15, 16, 37, 42,50, 51, 52, 53 y 54' WHEN 'A4' THEN 'Artículos 6, 15, 16, 37, 42,50, 51, 52, 53 y 54' WHEN 'PF' THEN 'Artículos 6, 15, 16, 37, 42,50, 51, 52, 53 y 54' WHEN 'OR' THEN 'Artículos 6, 15, 16, 37, 42,50, 51, 52, 53 y 54' WHEN 'A5' THEN 'Artículos 6, 15, 16, 37, 42,50, 51, 52, 53 y 54' WHEN 'A6' THEN 'Artículos 6, 15, 16, 37, 42,50, 51, 52, 53 y 54' END /*# sol_art_concesion */ FROM solicitud sol WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

select cip.seccion_CIP+cip.clase_CIP+cip.subclase_CIP+' '+cip.grupo_CIP+'/'+cip.subgrupo_CIP+' ('+{sol_fechaedicionCIP}+')' /*# sol_cip_clasif_princ*/ FROM solicitud sol, solicitud_cip cip WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join externo con CIP principal */ sol.COD_OFICINA = cip.COD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = cip.TIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = cip.SER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = cip.NUM_EXPED AND cip.CALIFICACION_CIP='A' AND CIP.EDICION_CIP=8

select cip.seccion_CIP+cip.clase_CIP+cip.subclase_CIP+' '+cip.grupo_CIP+'/'+cip.subgrupo_CIP+' ('+{sol_fechaedicionCIP}+')' /*# sol_cip_clasif_sec*/ FROM solicitud sol, solicitud_cip cip WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join externo con CIP principal */ sol.COD_OFICINA = cip.COD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = cip.TIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = cip.SER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = cip.NUM_EXPED AND cip.CALIFICACION_CIP='B' AND CIP.EDICION_CIP=8

SELECT RTRIM(NOM_PERSONA) /*# Creador_Nombre */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION ORDER BY S.NUM_ORDEN

SELECT CAST(dir_calle AS VARCHAR(256)) + CASE WHEN cast(dir_colonia as varchar(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_colonia AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(cod_postal as varchar(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(cod_postal AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', ' + CAST(Pa.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR(256)) END /*# Creador_Direccion */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais

ROW.SQL_NAME: Cada documento usado en examen de patentes
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT 'Categ: ' + CATEG_REFERENCIA + '. Reivin: ' + REF_REIVINDICACION + '. Docum: ' + DES_REFERENCIA /*# sol_examen_documentos */ FROM SOLICITUD_REF_EXAMEN WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED ORDER BY SEC_REF

SELECT CASE m.fec_movimiento WHEN NULL THEN NULL ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, m.fec_movimiento, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, m.fec_movimiento, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, m.fec_movimiento, 103)) END /*# sol_fec_cumple_exa_fondo */ FROM movimiento m, tramite t WHERE m.num_tramite = t.num_tramite AND m.tip_tramite = 'PAT' AND m.tip_movimiento = '040' AND t.cod_oficina_exped = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND t.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND t.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND t.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT /*to_char(T.fec_status,'dd/mm/yyyy')*/ /*# ofi_fecha_status */ CONVERT(VARCHAR, T.fec_status, 103) FROM oficio o, tramite T WHERE o.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND o.SER_OFICIO = :GVnSER_OFICIO AND o.NUM_OFICIO = :GVnNUM_OFICIO AND /* join con TRAMITE */ O.cod_oficina_OFICIO = T.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND o.tip_OFICIO = T.TIP_OFICIO AND O.ser_OFICIO = T.SER_OFICIO AND O.num_OFICIO = T.NUM_OFICIO AND T.tip_tramite =O.tip_tramite_OFICIO AND T.num_tramite =O.num_tramite_oficio

SELECT sub.des_subtipo +' no.: '+CONVERT(VARCHAR, sol.ser_exped) +RIGHT(('000000'+CONVERT(VARCHAR, sol.num_exped)), 6) +' denominado '+sol.titulo+ ' número de registro: '+ISNULL(CONVERT(VARCHAR, sol.num_concesion), 'en trámite') /*# sol_expedientes_rel */ FROM expediente_vinculo vin, solicitud sol, subtipo_solicitud sub WHERE vin.cod_oficina1 = sol.cod_oficina AND vin.tip_exped1 = sol.tip_exped AND vin.ser_exped1 = sol.ser_exped AND vin.num_exped1 = sol.num_exped AND sol.subtip_solicitud = sub.subtip_solicitud AND vin.COD_OFICINA2 = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND vin.TIP_EXPED2 = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND vin.SER_EXPED2 = :GVnSER_EXPED AND vin.NUM_EXPED2 = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT /* expediente */ /* expediente */ :GVstrCOD_OFICINA /*# sol_expediente_origen */, :GVstrTIP_EXPED /*# sol_expediente_tipo */, CAST(:GVnSER_EXPED AS int) /*# sol_expediente_serie */, CAST(:GVnNUM_EXPED AS int) /*# sol_expediente_numero */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, :GVnSER_EXPED) + '-'+ CONVERT(VARCHAR, :GVnNUM_EXPED) /*# sol_expediente */, /* fechas varias */ CONVERT(VARCHAR, fec_recepcion, 103) /*# sol_fec_recepcion_dma */, CONVERT(varchar, D.fec_recepcion, 108) /*# sol_hora_recepcion */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, e.fec_presentacion, 103) /*# sol_fec_presentacion_dma */, CASE e.fec_presentacion WHEN NULL THEN NULL ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, e.fec_presentacion, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, e.fec_presentacion, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, e.fec_presentacion, 103)) END /*# sol_fec_presentacion_texto */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, fec_publicacion, 103) /*# sol_fec_publicacion_dma */, CASE fec_publicacion WHEN NULL THEN NULL ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, fec_publicacion, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, fec_publicacion, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, fec_publicacion, 103)) END /*# sol_fec_publicacion_texto */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, fec_concesion, 103) /*# sol_fec_concesion_dma */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, fec_vigencia, 103) /*# sol_fec_vigencia_dma */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, fec_vencimiento, 103) /*# sol_fec_vencimiento_dma */, /* numero de concesion */ tip_concesion /*# sol_concesion_tipo */, ser_concesion /*# sol_concesion_serie */, num_concesion /*# sol_concesion_numero */, dup_concesion /*# sol_concesion_dup */ , /* tipo y subtipo */ DES_TIPO /*# sol_tipo */, DES_SUBTIPO /*# sol_subtipo */, /* apoderado */ CAST(per_apo.COD_DESPACHO as varchar) /*# sol_apoderado_numero */, RTRIM(per_apo.nom_persona) /*# sol_apoderado_nombre */, CAST(dir_apo.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_colonia IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_apo.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_apo.cod_postal IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_apo.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_poblacion IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_apo.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_apo.nom_estado IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_apo.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR) /*# sol_apoderado_direccion */, CAST(dir_apo.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_colonia IS null THEN NULL ELSE CHAR(13) + CAST(CHAR(10) AS VARCHAR) + CAST(dir_apo.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_apo.cod_postal IS null THEN NULL ELSE CHAR(13) + CAST(CHAR(10) AS VARCHAR) + CAST(dir_apo.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_poblacion IS null THEN NULL ELSE CHAR(13) + CAST(CHAR(10) AS VARCHAR) + CAST(dir_apo.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR) /*# sol_apoderado_dir_vert */, e.COD_GACETA_PUBL /*8*//*# sol_gaceta_cod */ FROM expediente e LEFT OUTER JOIN PERSONA per_apo ON e.COD_PERSONA_PRO = per_apo.COD_PERSONA LEFT OUTER JOIN PERSONA_DIREC dir_apo ON e.COD_PERSONA_PRO = dir_apo.COD_PERSONA AND e.SEC_DIRECCION_PRO = dir_apo.SEC_DIRECCION LEFT OUTER JOIN DESPACHO apo_desp ON per_apo.COD_DESPACHO = apo_desp.COD_DESPACHO , documento d, tipo_solicitud t_sol, subtipo_solicitud st_sol, PERSONA per_tit, PERSONA_DIREC dir_tit, PAIS pais_tit WHERE e.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND e.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND e.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND e.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND e.COD_OFICINA = d.SEC_EXPED AND e.TIP_LIBRO = d.TIP_LIBRO AND e.SER_DOCUM = d.SER_DOCUM AND e.NUM_DOCUM = d.NUM_DOCUM AND e.COD_PERSONA_TIT1 = per_tit.COD_PERSONA AND e.COD_PERSONA_TIT1 = dir_tit.COD_PERSONA AND e.SEC_DIRECCION_TIT1 = dir_tit.SEC_DIRECCION AND dir_tit.cod_pais_resid = cod_pais AND e.TIP_SOLICITUD = t_sol.TIP_SOLICITUD AND e.TIP_SOLICITUD = st_sol.TIP_SOLICITUD AND e.SUBTIP_SOLICITUD = st_sol.SUBTIP_SOLICITUD

SELECT DP.NUM_RECIBO /*# sol_numero_servicio*/ FROM solicitud sol, DOCUMENTO_PAGO DP WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA and sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED and sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED and sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED and sol.tip_libro= DP.TIP_LIBRO AND sol.NUM_DOCUM = DP.NUM_DOCUM AND sol.SER_DOCUM = DP.SER_DOCUM

SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR, T.fec_status, 103) /*# sol_status_fec */ , s.des_status /*# sol_status */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, T.fec_vencimiento, 103) /*# sol_status_fec_venc */, U.nombre /*# sol_responsable */ FROM expediente e, tramite T, status S, usuario U WHERE e.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND e.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND e.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND e.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con TRAMITE */ e.cod_oficina = T.COD_OFICINA_EXPED AND e.tip_exped = T.TIP_EXPED AND e.ser_exped = T.SER_EXPED AND e.num_exped = T.NUM_EXPED AND T.tip_tramite = S.tip_tramite AND T.cod_status = S.cod_status AND T.user_id_resp = U.user_id

SELECT DP.IMP_RECIBO /*# sol_tarifa*/ FROM solicitud sol, DOCUMENTO_PAGO DP WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA and sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED and sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED and sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED and sol.tip_libro= DP.TIP_LIBRO AND sol.NUM_DOCUM = DP.NUM_DOCUM AND sol.SER_DOCUM = DP.SER_DOCUM

SELECT /*decode( SS. IND_PCT,'S','X','') */ case SS. IND_PCT when 'S' then 'X' else '' end /*# sol_ind_pct*/ FROM Solicitud D, SUBTIPO_SOLICITUD SS WHERE D.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA and D.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED and D.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED and D.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED and D.TIP_SOLICITUD = SS.TIP_SOLICITUD AND D.SUBTIP_SOLICITUD = SS.SUBTIP_SOLICITUD

SELECT /* expediente */ g.DES_GACETA /* #sol_gaceta_des */ FROM expediente e, gaceta g WHERE e.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND e.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND e.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND e.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con gaceta */ e.COD_GACETA_PUBL = g.COD_GACETA

SELECT cast(T.DES_TIPO as varchar) /*# sol_modalidad*/ FROM expediente E, TIPO_EXPEDIENTE T WHERE e.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND e.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND e.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND e.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND T.TIP_EXPED = E.TIP_EXPED

ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CASE WHEN {sol_fec_vigencia_dma} IS NULL THEN NULL /*ELSE CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vigencia_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vigencia_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(DATEPART(YYYY, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vigencia_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) */ ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vigencia_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vigencia_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vigencia_dma}, 103)) END /*# sol_fec_vigencia_texto */, CASE WHEN {sol_fec_concesion_dma} IS NULL THEN NULL /*ELSE CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_concesion_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_concesion_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(DATEPART(YYYY, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_concesion_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) */ ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_concesion_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_concesion_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_concesion_dma}, 103)) END /*# sol_fec_concesion_texto */, CASE WHEN {sol_fec_vencimiento_dma} IS NULL THEN NULL /*ELSE CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vencimiento_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vencimiento_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(DATEPART(YYYY, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vencimiento_dma}, 103)) AS VARCHAR) */ ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vencimiento_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vencimiento_dma}, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, {sol_fec_vencimiento_dma}, 103)) END /*# sol_fec_vencimiento_texto */

SELECT RTRIM(NOM_PERSONA) /*# Inventor_Nombre */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION ORDER BY S.NUM_ORDEN

SELECT p.nom_persona /*# sol_inventor_nombre_vert */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ s.COD_PERSONA = p.COD_PERSONA AND s.COD_PERSONA = d.COD_PERSONA AND s.SEC_DIRECCION = d.SEC_DIRECCION AND /* join con pais */ cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais order by s.NUM_ORDEN

ROW.SQL_NAME: Nombre y dirección de cada inventor
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CAST(NOM_PERSONA AS VARCHAR(256)) + ' domiciliado en ' + CAST(dir_calle AS VARCHAR(256)) + CASE WHEN cast(dir_colonia as varchar(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_colonia AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(cod_postal as varchar(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(cod_postal AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', ' + CAST(Pa.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR(256)) END /*# sol_inventor_nombre_direccion */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais

ROW.SQL_NAME: Nombre y codigo país de cada inventor
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CAST(NOM_PERSONA AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', ' + CAST(Pa.COD_PAIS AS VARCHAR(10)) /*# sol_inventor_nombre_pais */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR S, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = p.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = d.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = d.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais ORDER BY S.num_orden

ROW.SQL_NAME: Nombre y codigo país de cada inventor
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT cast(NOM_PERSONA as varchar(256)) + ' (' + cast(Pa.COD_PAIS as varchar(256)) + ')' /*# sol_inventor_nombre_(pais) */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION AND /* join con pais */ cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais order by s.num_orden

SELECT CAST(NOM_PERSONA AS VARCHAR(256)) + ' domiciliado en ' + CAST(dir_calle AS VARCHAR(256)) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_colonia IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_colonia AS VARCHAR(256)) END AS VARCHAR(256)) + CAST( CASE WHEN cod_postal IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(cod_postal AS VARCHAR) END AS VARCHAR (256)) + CAST( CASE WHEN dir_poblacion IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) END AS VARCHAR(256)) + CAST( CASE WHEN d.nom_estado IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', ' + CAST(Pa.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR(256)) END AS VARCHAR(256)) + CAST( CASE WHEN p.telefono IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + ' telef : ' + CAST(p.telefono AS VARCHAR(256)) END AS VARCHAR(256)) + CAST( CASE WHEN p.email IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + ' email : ' + CAST(p.email AS VARCHAR(256)) END AS VARCHAR(256)) /*# sol_inventor_nombre_direcciontel*/ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = pa.cod_pais

SELECT CAST(dir_calle AS VARCHAR(256)) + CASE WHEN cast(dir_colonia as varchar(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_colonia AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(cod_postal as varchar(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(cod_postal AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) IS null THEN NULL ELSE ', ' + CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', ' + CAST(Pa.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR(256)) END /*# Inventor_Direccion */ FROM SOLICITUD_INVENTOR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais

(Adición)' THEN CASE {sol_decretoley} WHEN '0041' THEN CASE {sol_concesion} WHEN '//' THEN 'A7' ELSE 'B7' END ELSE 'A4' END WHEN 'Autor de invención PCT' THEN CASE {sol_decretoley} WHEN '0041' THEN CASE {sol_concesion} WHEN '//' THEN 'A6' ELSE 'B6' END ELSE 'A1' END WHEN 'Patente de Inv. PCT' THEN CASE {sol_decretoley} WHEN '0041' THEN CASE {sol_concesion} WHEN '//' THEN 'A7' ELSE 'B7' END ELSE 'A3' END WHEN 'Patente de Inv. divisional' THEN CASE {sol_decretoley} WHEN '0041' THEN CASE {sol_concesion} WHEN '//' THEN 'A7' ELSE 'A7' END ELSE 'A3' END WHEN 'Patente de Inv. PCT divisional' THEN CASE {sol_decretoley} WHEN '0041' THEN CASE {sol_concesion} WHEN '//' THEN 'A7' ELSE 'B7' END ELSE 'A3' END WHEN 'Autor de Inv. divisional' THEN CASE {sol_decretoley} WHEN '0041' THEN CASE {sol_concesion} WHEN '//' THEN 'A6' ELSE 'B6' END ELSE 'A1' END WHEN 'Autor de Inv. PCT divisional' THEN CASE {sol_decretoley} WHEN '0041' THEN CASE {sol_concesion} WHEN '//' THEN 'A6' ELSE 'B6' END ELSE 'A1' END WHEN 'Patente depósito' THEN 'A' WHEN 'Autor de Inv. Variedad Vegetal' THEN 'A1' WHEN 'Patente de Inv. Variedad Veget' THEN 'A3' WHEN 'Patente introducción' THEN 'A' WHEN 'Patente' THEN 'A' WHEN 'Autor de Modelo Industrial' THEN 'S1' WHEN 'Autor de Modelo Ind división' THEN 'S1' WHEN 'Patente de Modelo Industrial' THEN 'S2' WHEN 'Patente de Mod Ind divisional' THEN 'S2' WHEN 'Autor de Invención RM' THEN 'A5' WHEN 'Autor de Inv 805-DL68' THEN 'A1' WHEN 'Autor Modelo 805/DL68' THEN 'S1' WHEN 'Modelo Depósito' THEN 'S2' WHEN 'Modelo Introducción' THEN 'S2' WHEN 'Modelo' THEN 'S2' WHEN 'Autor de Inv 805-DL68' THEN 'A1' END /*# sol_publicacion */ FROM SOLICITUD s, TIPO_SOLICITUD ti, SUBTIPO_SOLICITUD su WHERE s.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND s.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND s.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND s.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND s.TIP_SOLICITUD = ti.TIP_SOLICITUD AND s.TIP_EXPED = ti.TIP_EXPED AND s.TIP_SOLICITUD = su.TIP_SOLICITUD AND s.SUBTIP_SOLICITUD = su.SUBTIP_SOLICITUD

SELECT cod_locarno /*# sol_locarno */
FROM SOLICITUD_LOCARNO WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT substring(cod_locarno,1,2) /*# sol_locarno_clase */
FROM SOLICITUD_LOCARNO WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT substring(cod_locarno,4,2) /*# sol_locarno_subclase */
FROM SOLICITUD_LOCARNO WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT O.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO /*# ofi_oficina */, O.SER_OFICIO /*# ofi_serie */, O.NUM_OFICIO /*# ofi_numero */, T.DES_OFICIO /*# ofi_tipo */ FROM OFICIO O, TIPO_OFICIO T WHERE O.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND O.SER_OFICIO = :GVnSER_OFICIO AND O.NUM_OFICIO = :GVnNUM_OFICIO AND /* join con tipo de oficio */ O.TIP_OFICIO = T.TIP_OFICIO

ROW.SQL_NAME: Datos de oficio para menú contextual
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT 'En fecha ' + /*to_char(FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 'fmdd')*/ DATENAME(day, fec_movimiento) + ' de ' + /*to_char(FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 'fmmonth')*/ DATENAME(month, fec_movimiento) + ' de ' + /*to_char(FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 'yyyy')*/ datename(year, fec_movimiento) + ', fue dictada Resolución No. ' + /*to_char(NUM_SECUENCIA,'000000')*/ RIGHT('000000'+CAST(NUM_SECUENCIA AS INT), 6) /*# menu_odoc_1 */ FROM OFICIO O, MOVIMIENTO M WHERE O.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND O.SER_OFICIO = :GVnSER_OFICIO AND O.NUM_OFICIO = :GVnNUM_OFICIO AND /* join con movimiento */ O.TIP_TRAMITE = M.TIP_TRAMITE AND O.NUM_TRAMITE = M.NUM_TRAMITE AND O.SEC_MOV = M.SEC_MOVIMIENTO

SELECT E.SER_EXPED /*# ofi_ser_exped */, E.NUM_EXPED /*# ofi_num_exped */, E.FEC_PRESENTACION /*# ofi_exp_fec_presentacion */, TE.DES_TIPO /*# ofi_exp_modalidad */, U.nombre /*# sol_responsable_oficio */ FROM OFICIO O, TRAMITE T, EXPEDIENTE E, TIPO_EXPEDIENTE TE, USUARIO U WHERE O.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND O.SER_OFICIO = :GVnSER_OFICIO AND O.NUM_OFICIO = :GVnNUM_OFICIO AND /* join con tramite */ O.TIP_TRAMITE_OFICIO = T.TIP_TRAMITE AND O.NUM_TRAMITE_OFICIO = T.NUM_TRAMITE AND /* join con expediente */ T.TIP_TRAMITE_SOLIC = E.TIP_TRAMITE AND T.NUM_TRAMITE_SOLIC = E.NUM_TRAMITE AND T.user_id_resp = U.user_id AND /*join con tipo expediente*/ TE.TIP_EXPED = E.TIP_EXPED ORDER BY TE.DES_TIPO

SELECT /*to_char(D.FEC_NOTIFICACION,'dd/mm/yyyy') */ CONVERT(varchar, D.fec_notificacion, 103) /*# ofi_fec_notificacion */ FROM DOCUMENTO D WHERE D.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND D.SER_OFICIO = :GVnSER_OFICIO AND D.NUM_OFICIO = :GVnNUM_OFICIO ORDER BY D.FEC_NOTIFICACION
SELECT M.OBS_MOVIMIENTO /*# ofi_num_resol */ FROM MOVIMIENTO M WHERE M.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND M.SER_OFICIO = :GVnSER_OFICIO AND M.NUM_OFICIO = :GVnNUM_OFICIO

ROW.SQL_NAME: Fecha de recepción en registro del oficio
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT /*to_char(R.FEC_ENTREGA,'dd/mm/yyyy')*/ convert(varchar, R.fec_entrega, 103) /*# ofi_fec_entrega */ FROM relacion_oficio RO, relacion R WHERE R.ser_relacion=RO.ser_relacion and R.num_relacion=RO.num_relacion and R.tip_relacion='O' and R.cod_depto='01' and RO.COD_OFICINA_OFICIO = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_OFICIO AND RO.SER_OFICIO = :GVnSER_OFICIO AND RO.NUM_OFICIO = :GVnNUM_OFICIO

SELECT TITULO /*1*//*# sol_titulo */, :GVstrCLASIFICACION_CIP /*2*//*# sol_cip */, 'Int.Cl.' + CAST(EDICION_CIP AS VARCHAR) /*3*//*# sol_cip_edicion */, EDICION_CIP /*4*//*# sol_cip_edicion_no */, /* datos PCT */ resumen /*5*//*# sol_resumen */, COD_PAIS_PUBL_PCT+ID_SOLICITUD_PCT /*6*//*# sol_pct_id_solicitud */, ID_PUBL_PCT /*7*//*# sol_pct_id_publicacion */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, FEC_PUBL_PCT, 103) /*8*//*# sol_pct_fec_publicacion_dma */, CASE FEC_PUBL_PCT WHEN NULL THEN NULL ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_PUBL_PCT, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_PUBL_PCT, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_PUBL_PCT, 103)) END /*9*//*# sol_pct_fec_publicacion_texto */, CONVERT(VARCHAR, FEC_SOLICITUD_PCT, 103)/*10*//*# sol_pct_fec_solicitud_dma */, /* datos del examen tecnico */ CASE FEC_SOLICITUD_PCT WHEN NULL THEN NULL ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_SOLICITUD_PCT, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_SOLICITUD_PCT, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_SOLICITUD_PCT, 103)) END /*11*//*# sol_pct_fec_solicitud_texto */, DES_CIP_EXAMEN /*12*//*# sol_examen_cip */, DES_CRITERIO_EXAMEN /*13*//*# sol_examen_palabras */, CASE IND_RESULTADO_NOVEDAD WHEN 'S' THEN 'Si' WHEN 'N' THEN 'No' ELSE 'N/A' END /*14*//*# sol_examen_res_novedad */ , CASE IND_RESULTADO_INVENTIVA WHEN 'S' THEN 'Si' WHEN 'N' THEN 'No' ELSE 'N/A' END /*15*//*# sol_examen_res_inventiva */, CASE IND_RESULTADO_INDUSTRIAL WHEN 'S' THEN 'Si' WHEN 'N' THEN 'No' ELSE 'N/A' END /*16*//*# sol_examen_res_industrial */, DES_SUGERENCIA /*17*//*# sol_notas */, cant_anios_concesion /*18*//*# sol_cant_anios_concesion */, CASE cant_anios_concesion WHEN 5 THEN 'Cinco' WHEN 15 THEN 'Quince' WHEN 20 THEN 'Veinte' ELSE 'N/A' END /*19*//*# sol_cant_anios_conc_letras */, CASE max_renovaciones WHEN 2 THEN 'con derecho a dos períodos' ELSE null END /*19*//*# sol_max_renovaciones */, CASE cant_anios_vigencia_renovacion WHEN 5 THEN ' prorrogables de cinco años cada uno' ELSE null END /*19*//*# sol_anios_prorrog */, cod_publicacion /*# sol_cod_publicacion */ FROM solicitud sol LEFT OUTER JOIN solicitud_resumen res ON sol.COD_OFICINA = res.COD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = res.TIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = res.SER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = res.NUM_EXPED AND 'MX' = res.cod_pais LEFT OUTER JOIN solicitud_cip cip ON sol.COD_OFICINA = cip.COD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = cip.TIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = cip.SER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = cip.NUM_EXPED AND 'A' = cip.calificacion_cip LEFT OUTER JOIN ley_subtipo_solicitud ley ON sol.cod_ley = ley.cod_ley AND sol.tip_solicitud = ley.tip_solicitud AND sol.subtip_solicitud = ley.subtip_solicitud WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

ROW.SQL_NAME: Calcula el número de folio de la inscripción
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT sol.num_concesion - (SELECT min(a.num_concesion)-1 FROM solicitud a WHERE a.ser_concesion = sol.ser_concesion GROUP BY a.ser_concesion) folio /*# sol_concesion_folio */ FROM solicitud sol WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED
SELECT resumen /*1*//*# sol_reservas */ FROM solicitud_resumen res WHERE res.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND res.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND res.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND res.cod_pais = 'US'

ROW.SQL_NAME: Fecha de la edición de la CIP
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: select fojas_descripcion /*# sol_fechaedicionCIP */ FROM solicitud sol WHERE sol.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND sol.TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND sol.SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND sol.NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT id_solicitud + ' - ' + CONVERT(varchar, fec_solicitud, 111) + ' - ' + cod_pais /*# sol_prioridades */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_PRIORIDAD WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND reconocida = 'S'

SELECT id_solicitud +' con fecha '+ datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, fec_solicitud, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, fec_solicitud, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, fec_solicitud, 103)) /*# sol_prioridades_texto */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_PRIORIDAD WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT /*to_char(FEC_SOLICITUD, 'yyyy/mm/dd' ) + ' ' + */ CONVERT(varchar, fec_solicitud, 111) + ' ' + COD_PAIS + ' ' + ID_SOLICITUD /*# sol_prioridades_N */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_PRIORIDAD WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND reconocida='N'

SELECT /*to_char(FEC_SOLICITUD, 'yyyy/mm/dd' ) + ' ' + */ CONVERT(varchar, fec_solicitud, 111) + ' ' + COD_PAIS + ' ' + ID_SOLICITUD /*# sol_prioridades_T */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_PRIORIDAD WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED

SELECT NOM_PERSONA /*# prom_titular_anterior_nombre */ FROM PROMOCION u, PROMOCION_ANTERIOR_TITULAR o, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE u.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrDOC_ORI AND u.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrDOC_LOG AND u.SER_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_SER AND u.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_NBR AND /* join with PROMOCION_ANTERIOR_TITULAR */ u.COD_OFICINA = o.COD_OFICINA_DOCUM AND u.TIP_LIBRO = o.TIP_LIBRO AND u.SER_DOCUM = o.SER_DOCUM AND u.NUM_DOCUM = o.NUM_DOCUM AND /* join with PERSONA and PERSONA_DIRECCION */ o.COD_PERSONA = p.COD_PERSONA AND o.COD_PERSONA = a.COD_PERSONA AND o.SEC_DIRECCION = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND /* join with residence country */ cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

SELECT case when CAST(a.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_calle)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_colonia)) end + case when CAST(a.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.cod_postal)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_poblacion)) end + case when CAST(a.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.nom_estado)) end + case when CAST(c.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(c.NOM_PAIS)) end /*# prom_titular_anterior_direccion */ FROM PROMOCION u, PROMOCION_ANTERIOR_TITULAR o, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE u.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrDOC_ORI AND u.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrDOC_LOG AND u.SER_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_SER AND u.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_NBR AND u.COD_OFICINA = o.COD_OFICINA_DOCUM AND u.TIP_LIBRO = o.TIP_LIBRO AND u.SER_DOCUM = o.SER_DOCUM AND u.NUM_DOCUM = o.NUM_DOCUM AND o.COD_PERSONA = p.COD_PERSONA AND o.COD_PERSONA = a.COD_PERSONA AND o.SEC_DIRECCION = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

ROW.SQL_NAME: Nombre y dirección de cada titular anterior
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CAST(NOM_PERSONA AS VARCHAR) + case when CAST(a.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_calle)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_colonia)) end + case when CAST(a.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.cod_postal)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_poblacion)) end + case when CAST(a.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.nom_estado)) end + case when CAST(c.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(c.NOM_PAIS)) end /*# prom_titular_anterior_nombre_dir */ FROM PROMOCION u, PROMOCION_ANTERIOR_TITULAR o, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE u.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrDOC_ORI AND u.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrDOC_LOG AND u.SER_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_SER AND u.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_NBR AND u.COD_OFICINA = o.COD_OFICINA_DOCUM AND u.TIP_LIBRO = o.TIP_LIBRO AND u.SER_DOCUM = o.SER_DOCUM AND u.NUM_DOCUM = o.NUM_DOCUM AND o.COD_PERSONA = p.COD_PERSONA AND o.COD_PERSONA = a.COD_PERSONA AND o.SEC_DIRECCION = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

select OBS3 /*# prom_acceder_o_denegar */, case when cast(OBS3 as varchar) = 'acceder' or cast(OBS3 as varchar) = 'Acceder' then 'SEGUNDO: El cambio que se dispone surte efectos a partir de la fecha de su anotación en la Oficina.' else '' end /*# prom_acceder_anotacion */, case when cast(OBS3 as varchar) = 'denegar' or cast(OBS3 as varchar) = 'Denegar' then '; se apercibe que contra la Resolución podrá interponer demanda en proceso administrativo ante la Sala de lo Civil y lo Administrativo del Tribunal Provincial Popular de La Habana, dentro del término de treinta días hábiles contados a partir del día siguiente de la notificación de la presente. ' else '' end /*# prom_noacceder_anotacion_noti */ FROM USUARIO U LEFT OUTER JOIN SUBDIRECCION SUBDIR ON U.COD_DIREC = SUBDIR.COD_DIREC AND U.COD_SUBDIREC = SUBDIR.COD_SUBDIREC LEFT OUTER JOIN DEPARTAMENTO DEP ON U.COD_DIREC = DEP.COD_DIREC AND U.COD_SUBDIREC = DEP.COD_SUBDIREC AND U.COD_DEPTO = DEP.COD_DEPTO , MOVIMIENTO M, TIPO_MOVIMIENTO T, DIRECCION DIR WHERE M.TIP_TRAMITE = :GVstrTIP_TRAMITE AND M.NUM_TRAMITE = :GVnNUM_TRAMITE AND M.SEC_MOVIMIENTO = :GVnSEC_MOVIMIENTO AND M.TIP_MOVIMIENTO = T.TIP_MOVIMIENTO AND M.USER_ID_CAPT = U.USER_ID AND U.COD_DIREC = DIR.COD_DIREC AND T.tip_movimiento='2013'

SELECT p.NOM_PERSONA /*# prom_solicitante_nombre */, CAST((case when cast(a.DIR_CALLE as varchar) is null then '' else cast(a.DIR_CALLE as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(a.DIR_COLONIA as varchar) is null then '' else ', '+ cast(a.DIR_COLONIA as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(a.DIR_POBLACION as varchar) is null then '' else ', ' + cast(a.DIR_POBLACION as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(a.NOM_ESTADO as varchar) is null then '' else ', '+ cast(a.NOM_ESTADO as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(c.NOM_PAIS as varchar) is null then '' else ', '+ cast(c.NOM_PAIS as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) /*# prom_solicitante_direccion */ FROM PROMOCION u,PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE u.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrDOC_ORI AND u.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrDOC_LOG AND u.SER_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_SER AND u.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_NBR AND /* join with PERSONA and PERSONA_DIRECCION */ u.COD_PERSONA_ACCION = p.COD_PERSONA AND u.COD_PERSONA_ACCION = a.COD_PERSONA AND u.SEC_DIRECCION_ACCION = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND /* join with residence country */ cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

SELECT p.NOM_PERSONA /*# prom_licenciante_nombre */, CAST((case when cast(a.DIR_CALLE as varchar) is null then '' else cast(a.DIR_CALLE as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(a.DIR_COLONIA as varchar) is null then '' else ', '+ cast(a.DIR_COLONIA as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(a.DIR_POBLACION as varchar) is null then '' else ', ' + cast(a.DIR_POBLACION as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(a.NOM_ESTADO as varchar) is null then '' else ', '+ cast(a.NOM_ESTADO as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) + CAST((case when cast(c.NOM_PAIS as varchar) is null then '' else ', '+ cast(c.NOM_PAIS as varchar) end) AS VARCHAR) /*# prom_licenciante_direccion */ FROM PROMOCION u,PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE u.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrDOC_ORI AND u.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrDOC_LOG AND u.SER_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_SER AND u.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_NBR AND /* join with PERSONA and PERSONA_DIRECCION */ u.COD_PERSONA_LICENCIANTE = p.COD_PERSONA AND u.COD_PERSONA_LICENCIANTE = a.COD_PERSONA AND u.SEC_DIRECCION_LICENCIANTE = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND /* join with residence country */ cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

SELECT p.NOM_PERSONA /*# prom_licenciatario_nombre */, case when CAST(a.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_calle)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_colonia)) end + case when CAST(a.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.cod_postal)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_poblacion)) end + case when CAST(a.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.nom_estado)) end + case when CAST(c.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(c.NOM_PAIS)) end /*# prom_licenciatario_direccion */ FROM PROMOCION u,PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE u.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrDOC_ORI AND u.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrDOC_LOG AND u.SER_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_SER AND u.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_NBR AND /* join with PERSONA and PERSONA_DIRECCION */ u.COD_PERSONA_LICENCIATARIA = p.COD_PERSONA AND u.COD_PERSONA_LICENCIATARIA = a.COD_PERSONA AND u.SEC_DIRECCION_LICENCIATARIA = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND /* join with residence country */ cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

SELECT NOM_PERSONA /*# prom_titular_nuevo_nombre */, case when CAST(a.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_calle)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_colonia)) end + case when CAST(a.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.cod_postal)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_poblacion)) end + case when CAST(a.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.nom_estado)) end + case when CAST(c.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(c.NOM_PAIS)) end /*# prom_titular_nuevo_direccion */ FROM PROMOCION u, PROMOCION_CAMBIO_TITULAR o, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE u.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrDOC_ORI AND u.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrDOC_LOG AND u.SER_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_SER AND u.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnDOC_NBR AND u.COD_OFICINA = o.COD_OFICINA AND u.TIP_LIBRO = o.TIP_LIBRO AND u.SER_DOCUM = o.SER_DOCUM AND u.NUM_DOCUM = o.NUM_DOCUM AND o.COD_PERSONA = p.COD_PERSONA AND o.COD_PERSONA = a.COD_PERSONA AND o.SEC_DIRECCION = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

SELECT P.SEC_ANUALIDAD /*# prom_anualidad */ FROM PROMOCION_ANUALIDAD P WHERE P.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM and P.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO and P.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM and P.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM

SELECT RTRIM(NOM_PERSONA) /*# Titular_Nombre */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION

SELECT case when CAST(d.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else LTRIM(RTRIM(d.dir_calle)) end + case when CAST(d.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(d.dir_colonia)) end + case when CAST(d.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(d.cod_postal)) end + case when CAST(d.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(d.dir_poblacion)) end + case when CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(d.nom_estado)) end + case when CAST(pa.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(pa.NOM_PAIS)) end /*# Titular_Direccion */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais

ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CAST(NOM_PERSONA AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', con domicilio (legal) en ' + CAST(dir_calle AS VARCHAR(256)) + CASE WHEN dir_colonia IS null THEN '' ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_colonia AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN cod_postal IS null THEN '' ELSE ', ' + CAST(cod_postal AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN dir_poblacion IS null THEN '' ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR(256)) END + CASE WHEN d.nom_estado IS null THEN '' ELSE ', ' + CAST(d.nom_estado AS VARCHAR(256)) END + ', ' + CAST(Pa.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR(256)) + '' /*# sol_titular_nombre_direccion */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais

ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CAST(NOM_PERSONA AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', con domicilio (legal) en ' + case when CAST(a.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_calle)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_colonia)) end + case when CAST(a.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.cod_postal)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_poblacion)) end + case when CAST(a.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.nom_estado)) end + case when CAST(c.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(c.NOM_PAIS)) end /*# sol_titular_nombre_direcc_cod1 */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = a.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CAST(NOM_PERSONA AS VARCHAR(256)) + ', domiciliado en ' + case when CAST(a.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_calle)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_colonia)) end + case when CAST(a.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.cod_postal)) end + case when CAST(a.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.dir_poblacion)) end + case when CAST(a.nom_estado AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(a.nom_estado)) end + case when CAST(c.NOM_PAIS AS VARCHAR) is null then '' else ', ' + LTRIM(RTRIM(c.NOM_PAIS)) end /*# sol_titular_nombre_direcc_cod */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p, PERSONA_DIREC a, PAIS c WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = a.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = a.SEC_DIRECCION AND cod_pais_resid = c.cod_pais

ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT cast(NOM_PERSONA as varchar(256)) + ' (' + cast(Pa.COD_PAIS as varchar(256)) + ')' /*# sol_titular_nombre_(pais) */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d, PAIS Pa WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ s.COD_PERSONA = p.COD_PERSONA AND s.COD_PERSONA = d.COD_PERSONA AND s.SEC_DIRECCION = d.SEC_DIRECCION AND /* join con pais */ cod_pais_resid = Pa.cod_pais

SELECT d.dir_poblacion /*# sol_titular_municipio */ FROM VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d WHERE COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA AND TIP_EXPED = :GVstrTIP_EXPED AND SER_EXPED = :GVnSER_EXPED AND NUM_EXPED = :GVnNUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION = D.SEC_DIRECCION

ROW.SQL_NAME: Datos de promocion para menú contextual
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), FEC_PRESENTACION) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), FEC_PRESENTACION) AS VARCHAR) + ' de ' + CAST(DATEPART(YYYY, FEC_PRESENTACION) AS VARCHAR) /*# menu_udoc_1 */ FROM PROMOCION P, DOCUMENTO D WHERE P.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM AND P.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO AND P.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM AND P.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM AND D.COD_OFICINA = P.COD_OFICINA AND D.TIP_LIBRO = P.TIP_LIBRO AND D.SER_DOCUM = P.SER_DOCUM AND D.NUM_DOCUM = P.NUM_DOCUM

SELECT CAST(P.COD_OFICINA AS VARCHAR) + '/' + CAST(P.SER_DOCUM AS VARCHAR) + '/' + CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), P.NUM_DOCUM) AS VARCHAR) /*# prom_documento */, t.tip_promocion /*# prom_tipo */, tip_promo.DES_tipo /*# prom_tipo_nombre */, P.NUM_RECIBO /*# prom_recibo_numero */, /*to_char(P.FEC_RECIBO, 'dd/mm/yyyy' )*/ CONVERT(varchar, p.fec_recibo, 103) /*# prom_recibo_fecha */, P.IMP_RECIBO /*# prom_recibo_importe */, /*to_char(D.FEC_PROCESO, 'dd/mm/yyyy')*/ CONVERT(varchar, d.fec_proceso, 103) /*# prom_fec_presentacion_dma */, datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, d.fec_proceso, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, d.fec_proceso, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, d.fec_proceso, 103)) /*# prom_fec_presentacion_texto */, /* apoderado */ per_apo.nom_persona /*# prom_apoderado_nombre */, CASE WHEN CAST(dir_apo.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) IS null THEN '' ELSE CAST(dir_apo.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) END + CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_colonia IS null THEN '' ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_apo.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) END + CASE WHEN dir_apo.cod_postal IS null THEN '' ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_apo.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) END + CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_poblacion IS null THEN '' ELSE ', ' + CAST(dir_apo.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) END /*# prom_apoderado_direccion */, CASE WHEN CAST(dir_apo.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) IS null THEN '' ELSE CAST(dir_apo.dir_calle AS VARCHAR) END + CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_colonia IS null THEN '' ELSE CHAR(13) + CAST(CHAR(10) AS VARCHAR) + CAST(dir_apo.dir_colonia AS VARCHAR) END + CASE WHEN dir_apo.cod_postal IS null THEN '' ELSE CHAR(13) + CAST(CHAR(10) AS VARCHAR) + CAST(dir_apo.cod_postal AS VARCHAR) END + CASE WHEN dir_apo.dir_poblacion IS null THEN '' ELSE CHAR(13) + CAST(CHAR(10) AS VARCHAR) + CAST(dir_apo.dir_poblacion AS VARCHAR) END /*# prom_apoderado_dir_vert */, CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), per_apo.cod_despacho) /*# prom_apoderado_codigo */, apo_desp.OBS_DESPACHO /*# prom_consultoria */ FROM PROMOCION P LEFT OUTER JOIN PROMOCION_APODERADO P_APO ON P.COD_OFICINA = P_APO.COD_OFICINA AND P.TIP_LIBRO = P_APO.TIP_LIBRO AND P.SER_DOCUM = P_APO.SER_DOCUM AND P.NUM_DOCUM = P_APO.NUM_DOCUM LEFT OUTER JOIN PERSONA per_apo ON P_APO.COD_PERSONA = per_apo.COD_PERSONA LEFT OUTER JOIN PERSONA_DIREC dir_apo ON P_APO.COD_PERSONA = dir_apo.COD_PERSONA AND P_APO.SEC_DIRECCION = dir_apo.SEC_DIRECCION LEFT OUTER JOIN DESPACHO apo_desp ON per_apo.COD_DESPACHO = apo_desp.COD_DESPACHO, DOCUMENTO D, PROMOCION_TIPO t, TIPO_PROMOCION tip_promo WHERE P.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM AND P.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO AND P.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM AND P.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM AND D.COD_OFICINA = P.COD_OFICINA AND D.TIP_LIBRO = P.TIP_LIBRO AND D.SER_DOCUM = P.SER_DOCUM AND D.NUM_DOCUM = P.NUM_DOCUM AND T.COD_OFICINA = D.COD_OFICINA AND T.TIP_LIBRO = D.TIP_LIBRO AND T.SER_DOCUM = D.SER_DOCUM AND T.NUM_DOCUM = D.NUM_DOCUM AND T.tip_promocion = tip_promo.tip_promocion

SELECT CAST(P.SER_DOCUM AS VARCHAR) + '/' + CAST(CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), P.NUM_DOCUM) AS VARCHAR), /*# prom_documentoact */ CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), D.FEC_PROCESO, 103), /*# prom_fec_presentacion_dmaact*/ DE.ser_exped, /*# prom_serie_expedact*/ DE.num_exped, /*# prom_numero_expedact*/ TP.des_tipo /*#prom_descripcionact*/ FROM PROMOCION P, DOCUMENTO D, DOCUMENTO_EXPEDIENTE DE, TIPO_PROMOCION TP, PROMOCION_TIPO PT WHERE P.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM AND P.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO AND P.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM AND P.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM AND D.COD_OFICINA = P.COD_OFICINA AND D.TIP_LIBRO = P.TIP_LIBRO AND D.SER_DOCUM = P.SER_DOCUM AND D.NUM_DOCUM = P.NUM_DOCUM AND D.NUM_DOCUM = DE.NUM_DOCUM AND D.SER_DOCUM = DE.SER_DOCUM AND PT.tip_promocion = TP.tip_promocion AND PT.NUM_DOCUM = D.NUM_DOCUM AND PT.SER_DOCUM = D.SER_DOCUM ORDER BY P.NUM_DOCUM

SELECT /*to_char(DE.ser_exped)*/ CAST(DE.ser_exped AS VARCHAR) + ' - ' + /*to_char(DE.NUM_EXPED)*/ CAST(DE.num_exped AS VARCHAR) /*# prom_exp_afectados */ FROM DOCUMENTO_EXPEDIENTE DE WHERE DE.COD_OFICINA_DOCUM = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM and DE.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO and DE.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM and DE.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM

SELECT DF.DES_DELEGACION /*# prom_exped_delegacion */ FROM DOCUMENTO_EXPEDIENTE DE, DOCUMENTO D, DELEGACION_FEDERAL DF WHERE DE.COD_OFICINA_DOCUM = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM and DE.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO and DE.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM and DE.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM and DE.TIP_EXPED = D.TIP_EXPED AND DE.SER_EXPED = D. SER_EXPED AND DE.NUM_EXPED = D. NUM_EXPED AND DF.COD_DELEGACION = D.COD_DELEGACION

ROW.SQL_NAME: Nombre del titular del expediente afectado por la promocion
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT P.NOM_PERSONA /*# prom_titular_nombre */ FROM DOCUMENTO_EXPEDIENTE DE, VISTA_SOLICITUD_TITULAR s, PERSONA p , PERSONA_DIREC d WHERE DE.COD_OFICINA_DOCUM = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM AND DE.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO AND DE.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM AND DE.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM AND /* join con solicitud_titular */ s.TIP_EXPED=DE.TIP_EXPED AND s.SER_EXPED=DE.SER_EXPED AND S.NUM_EXPED=DE.NUM_EXPED AND /* join con persona y direccion */ S.COD_PERSONA = P.COD_PERSONA AND S.COD_PERSONA = D.COD_PERSONA AND S.SEC_DIRECCION= D.SEC_DIRECCION

SELECT cast(g.NUM_RECIBO as varchar) /*# prom_numero_recibo */ FROM PROMOCION P, DOCUMENTO D, DOCUMENTO_PAGO g WHERE P.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM and P.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO and P.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM and P.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM and /* join con documento */ D.COD_OFICINA = P.COD_OFICINA AND D.TIP_LIBRO = P.TIP_LIBRO AND D.SER_DOCUM = P.SER_DOCUM AND D.NUM_DOCUM = P.NUM_DOCUM AND /*JOIN con documento_pago*/ g.NUM_DOCUM=D.NUM_DOCUM AND g.SER_DOCUM=D.SER_DOCUM

SELECT DP.imp_recibo /*# prom_recibo_importeact */ FROM PROMOCION P, DOCUMENTO D, DOCUMENTO_PAGO DP WHERE P.COD_OFICINA = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM and P.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO and P.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM and P.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM and /* join con documento */ D.COD_OFICINA = P.COD_OFICINA AND D.TIP_LIBRO = P.TIP_LIBRO AND D.SER_DOCUM = P.SER_DOCUM AND D.NUM_DOCUM = P.NUM_DOCUM AND /*JOIN con documento_pago*/ DP.NUM_DOCUM=D.NUM_DOCUM AND DP.SER_DOCUM=D.SER_DOCUM

ROW.SQL_NAME: Modalidad del expediente afectado por la promocion
ROW.SENTENCE_TEXT: SELECT TE.DES_TIPO /*# prom_exp_modalidad*/ FROM DOCUMENTO_EXPEDIENTE DE, TIPO_EXPEDIENTE TE WHERE DE.COD_OFICINA_DOCUM = :GVstrCOD_OFICINA_DOCUM and DE.TIP_LIBRO = :GVstrTIP_LIBRO and DE.SER_DOCUM = :GVnSER_DOCUM and DE.NUM_DOCUM = :GVnNUM_DOCUM and /*join con tipo_expediente*/ TE.TIP_EXPED = DE.TIP_EXPED

SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR(23), FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 103)/*# Movimiento_Fecha_DMA */, CASE FEC_MOVIMIENTO WHEN NULL THEN NULL ELSE datename(day, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 103))+' de '+datename(month, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 103))+' de '+datename(year, CONVERT(DATETIME, FEC_MOVIMIENTO, 103)) END /*# Movimiento_Fecha_Texto */,
